NK039(ti)011:1: // gsung 'thor bu mu tig phreng ba las lha mo'i
NK039(ti)011:2: gsol mchod nyung ngur bsdus pa bzhugs so na mo
NK039(ti)011:3: gu ru d+h+we wa d+aaki ni h'u gsang sngags zab
NK039(ti)011:4: mo'i b+ha ga kun bzang ma yang gsang dngos grub
NK039(ti)011:5: mchog brnyes mtsho rgyal ma klong yangs zag med gter
NK039(ti)011:6: mdzod dbyangs can ma ma rgyud mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la
NK039(ti)011:7: 'dud do ma khyed ni blo gros rta bdun rgyas
NK039(ti)011:8: pa'i ma mi bzad tsha zer phyogs bcur 'gyed pa'i
NK039(ti)011:9: ma bdag blo'i ge sar phyogs bcur bskyed cig ma
NK039(ti)011:10: kho bos ma bskang nyung ngur gsol lo ma zhes
NK039(ti)011:11: dpal ldan lha mo la ji ltar mkho ba'i yo
NK039(ti)011:12: byad dam rdzas tshang bar bsags la rnal 'byor spros
NK039(ti)011:13: pa la dga' na dam pa rin po ches byas
NK039(ti)011:14: pa'i las byang gi dbyangs bzhin rol mo dang bcas
NK039(ti)011:15: pas b+h+yo ma g.yos byang shar me rlung gting gi
NK039(ti)011:16: rung ma bkod khrag mtsho rba rlabs g.yo ba'i dbus
NK039(ti)011:17: ma brtsegs thod mkhar dgu rim gzhal yas nas ma
NK039(ti)011:18: cig dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti ma lus
NK039(ti)011:19: bran dang g.yog 'khor bcas pa rnams ma thogs gnas
NK039(ti)011:20: 'dir myur du gshegs su gsol ma nyid thugs rjes
NK039(ti)011:21: brtse ba'i bdag nyid ma ma gzigs yal bar dor
NK039(ti)011:22: na su la re ma 'khrugs 'dod khams dbang phyug
NK039(ti)011:23: 'khor bcas kyis ma ltar byams shing sring ltar brtse
NK039(ti)011:24: bar mdzod ma g.yel ma g.yel dpal ldan re ma
NK039(ti)011:25: ti ma 'chug rnal 'byor bdag gi grogs mdzod cig
NK039(ti)011:26: ma la mchod pa 'bul ba'i yo byad ni ma
NK039(ti)011:27: bslad me tog bdug spos dri zhal rol ma spangs
NK039(ti)011:28: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya'i tshogs ma tshang med
NK039(ti)011:29: pa'i sman gtor rak+ta 'dis ma mo nag mo 'khor
NK039(ti)011:30: bcas thugs dam bskang ma nyams mkha' lding zangs mchu
NK039(ti)011:31: gser mig lug ma breg tsa ra sha chen gsur
NK039(ti)011:32: chen dri ma sbags shel sgong bdud rtsi rnam lnga'i
NK039(ti)011:33: tshogs ma tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang
NK039(ti)011:34: ma 'gran rdzu 'phrul shugs chen bong bu drel ma
NK039(ti)011:35: rung seng ge sbrul gyi snyan cha rgyan ma bzos
NK039(ti)011:36: mgo phreng g.yang gzhi nad rkyal 'dis ma sring mkha'
NK039(ti)011:37: 'gro'i tshogs kyis thugs dam bskang ma sgrib nyi zla'i
NK039(ti)011:38: lte rgyan dbu rgyan bcas ma rtsol glang chen ko
NK039(ti)011:39: rlon re lde'i gos ma bsags nor bu skyugs pa'i
NK039(ti)011:40: ne'u le 'dis ma dang srung mar bcas pa'i thugs
NK039(ti)011:41: dam bskang ma gyur 'gro ba gtor mar sbyar ba
NK039(ti)011:42: dang ma btsos chang dang mam sa tsit+ta'i khrag ma
NK039(ti)011:43: nor mchod rdzas rgya mtsho du ma 'dis ma 'khor
NK039(ti)011:44: sprul par bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang ma 'gyangs myur
NK039(ti)011:45: du sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor la ma sgrub dngos grub
NK039(ti)011:46: sna tshogs char phob cig ma thub yid la brnags
NK039(ti)011:47: pa'i bstan dgra kun ma bzhag da lta nyid du
NK039(ti)011:48: sod la shog ma chen srin po khros pa lha
NK039(ti)011:49: mo'i sku ma 'gags b+h+yo dang a ra li yi
NK039(ti)011:50: gsung ma 'dzin mtha' bral phyogs lhung yangs pa'i thugs
NK039(ti)011:51: ma yengs lha mo'i sku gsung thugs la bstod h'uh
NK039(ti)011:52: ma h+aa gu ru'i bstan srung dgongs su gsol ma
NK039(ti)011:53: rig dbang gis mkha' 'gro'i thugs dang 'gal ma brtson
NK039(ti)011:54: dus kyi sgrub pa chags pa dang ma gsal ting
NK039(ti)011:55: 'dzin g.yel ba mthol lo bshags ma bsten spyod pa
NK039(ti)011:56: tshul bzhin ma rtogs dang ma shes le lo som
NK039(ti)011:57: nyi zos pa'i mthus ma bshags gsang dang sba bar
NK039(ti)011:58: gyur pa dang ma tshogs bsnyen pa grangs las chags
NK039(ti)011:59: pa bshags ma 'byor dbang gis mchod pa rgyud chung
NK039(ti)011:60: dang ma gtsang phud nyams 'gal 'khrul snang la sogs
NK039(ti)011:61: ma dag nyes pa'i tshogs rnams ci mchis pa ma
NK039(ti)011:62: dmigs klong yongs ngang du bshags par bgyi e ma
NK039(ti)011:63: / ma bzhin skyongs mdzad lha mo'i bskang ba 'di
NK039(ti)011:64: ma nus 'khos chung byang chub rgyal mtshan khos ma
NK039(ti)011:65: log dad pas nyams su len pa dang ma dad
NK039(ti)011:66: skye bo ha bgad byed rten lags ma bzhugs 'das
NK039(ti)011:67: pa seng ge rgyal mtshan sogs ma sogs mang po'i
NK039(ti)011:68: bstan bcos brtsams par rigs ma 'khor 'das kyang skal
NK039(ti)011:69: bzang yid 'phrog nas ma 'ongs rnal 'byor pas kyang
NK039(ti)011:70: de bzhin mdzod ces sprang po'i yang mtha' ru gyur
NK039(ti)011:71: pa byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis yos lor rta zla'i
NK039(ti)011:72: nyi shu dgur rmi lam dag snang 'ga' zhig la
NK039(ti)011:74: ma chen bskang bsdus bzhugs so h'uh ma skyes ma
NK039(ti)011:75: 'gags chos kyi dbyings nyid las ma rung 'dul mdzad
NK039(ti)011:76: che mchog srin po'i gzugs ma cig zhal gsum phyag
NK039(ti)011:77: drug zhabs bzhi bsgrad ma chen he ru ka yi
NK039(ti)011:78: thugs dam bskang gtso mo yum chen mkha' 'gro bkrag
NK039(ti)011:79: gsal mkha' 'gro rnam gsal mkha' 'gro 'od gsal mkha'
NK039(ti)011:80: 'gro mnyen gsal mkha' 'gro yang gsal h'uh gtso mo
NK039(ti)011:81: 'dod khams mthing nag 'jigs pa'i sku lha mo dbu
NK039(ti)011:82: zhal ral pas stong khams khyab srin mo'i chas can
NK039(ti)011:83: g.yang gzhi ba dan bsnams dpal mo phud bdag ma
NK039(ti)011:84: yi thugs dam bskang nyi zla thod phreng rdo rje
NK039(ti)011:85: khrag 'thung khros ma'i rin chen khrag 'thung khros ma'i
NK039(ti)011:86: pad+ma khrag 'thung khros ma'i las kyi khrag 'thung khros
NK039(ti)011:87: ma'i mtshan gyi dbang phyug ma'i srid pa rgyal byed
NK039(ti)011:88: ma yi bdag nyid chen mo'i gcig pu chen mo'i
NK039(ti)011:89: srid pa shar gyi bdag mo'i srid pa lho yi
NK039(ti)011:90: bdag mo'i thugs dam bskang srid pa nub kyi bdag
NK039(ti)011:91: mo'i thugs dam bskang srid pa byang gi bdag mo'i
NK039(ti)011:92: thugs dam bskang h'uh dpal ldan lha mo mthing nag
NK039(ti)011:93: bong bu bcibs dpal gyi dbu la rma bya'i rgyal
NK039(ti)011:94: mtshan phyar dpal 'bar phyag gnyis ral gri nad rkyal
NK039(ti)011:95: 'dzin dpal 'byor lha mo chen mo'i thugs dam bskang
NK039(ti)011:96: khol mo nag mo'i re ma ti yi ba glang
NK039(ti)011:97: nag mo'i khri sman pi la'i re ma dza yi
NK039(ti)011:98: re ma dzi yi re ma dzu yi khrag 'thung
NK039(ti)011:99: chen mo'i sbyor bdag chen mo'i srog bdag chen mo'i
NK039(ti)011:100: khri za stong sgrol thugs dam bskang h'uh stobs ldan
NK039(ti)011:101: srin mo chen mo shams shams mo rigs ldan zhing
NK039(ti)011:102: lpags rlon pa'i na bza' gsol mthu ldan mi mgo
NK039(ti)011:103: swa phreng phyag na bsnams dam ldan a phyi chen
NK039(ti)011:104: mo'i thugs dam bskang yang phyi chen mo'i e ka
NK039(ti)011:105: tsa ti'i nam mkha'i rgyal mo'i gling bzhi spyi phud
NK039(ti)011:107: rdo rje sgeg mo'i sa bdag chen mo'i h'uh lha
NK039(ti)011:108: mo byang shar mtshams kyi gru 'degs ma lha mchog
NK039(ti)011:109: sku la zhing chen g.yang gzhi gsol lha tshogs kun
NK039(ti)011:110: kyang dur khrod chas kyis brgyan lha mo har ting
NK039(ti)011:111: dkar mo'i thugs dam bskang dun ting nag mo'i shan
NK039(ti)011:112: ting dmar mo'i thugs dam bskang grub ting ser mo'i
NK039(ti)011:113: dkar mo mche gtsigs sngon mo kha ha la dmar
NK039(ti)011:114: mo mchu 'jib ser mo rkang ldag lha yi srin
NK039(ti)011:115: mo'i gshin rje'i sring mo'i thugs dam bskang klu yi
NK039(ti)011:116: sring mo'i gnod sbyin sring mo'i h'uh dur khrod bdag
NK039(ti)011:117: mo mi srun 'jigs pa'i sku rgya mtsho chen po
NK039(ti)011:118: 'khrugs pa'i klong na bzhugs shugs 'gro'i gtso mo ri
NK039(ti)011:119: rab bsnyil stobs can kun grags chen mo rngams pa'i
NK039(ti)011:120: thugs dam bskang kun tu bzang mo'i thugs dam bskang
NK039(ti)011:121: rdo rje kun gsal thugs dam bskang ye shes mchog
NK039(ti)011:122: gi thugs dam bskang rdo rje 'od chags rdo rje
NK039(ti)011:123: gsal ba'i rdo rje g.yu sgron h'uh phyi rim lcags
NK039(ti)011:124: ri 'bar ba'i bskor ba la phyi 'khor dbang phyug
NK039(ti)011:125: nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang phyi rim skyong ba'i brtan
NK039(ti)011:126: ma bcu gnyis sogs phyi mo ma sring sum brgya'i
NK039(ti)011:127: thugs dam bskang h'uh ma chen la sogs 'khor bcas
NK039(ti)011:128: bskang ba'i rdzas dmar chen khrag gi mchod yon rgya
NK039(ti)011:129: mtsho dang mchog chen dbang po lnga yi me tog
NK039(ti)011:130: dang tshil chen rab tu bsreg pa'i bdug spos dang
NK039(ti)011:131: zhun chen rkang mar bstams pa'i mar me dang stobs
NK039(ti)011:132: chen ko ro tsa na'i dri chab dang sha chen
NK039(ti)011:133: rus par bcas pa'i zhal zas dang rkang chen thod
NK039(ti)011:134: rnga gsang ba'i rnge'u chung rol rlabs chen tshogs dang
NK039(ti)011:135: rmad byung gtor ma dang dpal chen sman dang bskang
NK039(ti)011:136: rdzas rgyun gtor dang chas chen mgo phreng zhing lpags
NK039(ti)011:137: g.yang gzhi dang glang chen ko rlon stag shams sbrul
NK039(ti)011:138: chun dang ngar chen tsa ra mkha' lding zangs mchu
NK039(ti)011:139: dang thal chen tshom bu zhag gi zo ris dang
NK039(ti)011:140: sman chen lnga sogs mchod rdzas rgya mtsho 'dis dpal
NK039(ti)011:141: chen khyed rnams thugs dam bskang gyur cig khur chen
NK039(ti)011:142: khyer ba'i rnal 'byor 'khor bcas kyis theg chen lta
NK039(ti)011:143: ba klong du ma gyur dang lung chen bsnyen pa
NK039(ti)011:144: grangs las chags pa dang gsang chen dam med mi
NK039(ti)011:145: la spel ba dang dus chen mchod gtor chags pa
NK039(ti)011:146: mthol lo bshags theg chen g.yar dam nyams pa ci
NK039(ti)011:147: mchis pa klong chen zang thal ngang du bshags par
NK039(ti)011:148: bgyi e ma / ma chen bskang ba nyung ngur
NK039(ti)011:149: bkod pa 'di tshul min khengs sems rlom pa ma
NK039(ti)011:150: yin zhing bka' brgyud gong ma'i bka' srol yin phyir
NK039(ti)011:151: ro tshing nyung don la dbyer med gcig pa 'di
NK039(ti)011:152: ston pa'i bka' la bsre bslad ma yin zhing rang
NK039(ti)011:153: 'dra'i blo chung rgyun khyer bde phyir ro ma mo
NK039(ti)011:154: dpal ldan lha mo'i tshig rgyan 'di che mtho mkhas
NK039(ti)011:155: 'dod byed pa ma yin zhing rnal lam snang bar
NK039(ti)011:156: re ma ti'i wak+ka de ltar mthong ba'i rtags tshad
NK039(ti)011:157: mi ldan na kho bo dman pa'i gang zag ma
NK039(ti)011:158: yin zhing bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rang rtags shar phyir
NK039(ti)011:159: ro 'di dang 'di 'dra'i legs bshad phreng ba kun
NK039(ti)011:160: rang mtho'i nga rgyal gleng ba ma yin zhing tshad
NK039(ti)011:161: gsum gzhung la 'gal ba med phyir ro de phyir
NK039(ti)011:162: slad nas 'byon pa'i rnal 'byor kun de na 'di
NK039(ti)011:163: la the tshom mi byed cing mkhas rmongs gang gis
NK039(ti)011:164: nyams su len par zhu zhes tshig rgyan la mngon
NK039(ti)011:165: par phyogs pa'i khol ri pa byang chub rgyal mtshan
NK039(ti)011:166: gyis yos lo lug zla'i tshes gcig la gnas mchog
